m for financial gain at the expense of others.  Take heart that this is a VAST minority of players, and that thousands of successful and pleasant transactions take place daily.  Yes!  You too can be scammed out of 500p!  Yes!  You too can get smeared tomorrow by a drunk driver.  <br>
<br>
@#%$ happens, protect yourself from it when you can, do something about it instead of just bitching, or just take a stfu pill and live your life.<br>
<br>
BTW, i don't think i'll be changing my name, I rather like it.<br>
