Heck, it might even allow a few people to start fresh and do good with it. <br>
<br>
And it will definately allow some people who have run into the wrong element and can't shake it, to shake it.<br>
<br>
And some people just might want to change their name because they really got sick of the old one. <br>
<br>
Of course all this brings to mind the day that Homer Simpson became Max Power...How many scammers do you think will scrape together the $50 and then go out with overconfidence and ruin the rep of their new name.<br>
